        <abstract> 
<p>JDH has sent a short-styled <hi rend="italic">Forsythia</hi> from Kew. CD surmises that all <hi rend="italic">Forsythia</hi> at Kew may be short-styled, hence he is curious to know whether they set seed.</p> 
